title: Tuscan Sausage and Pepper Spaghetti Tuscan Sausage and Pepper Spaghetti
description: Does your love for pasta know no bounds? Well, here’s a recipe that’s sure to please anyone who is a nut for noodles. Slivers of bell pepper, crumbled pork sausage, and a flavorful tomato sauce are tossed with spaghetti, coming together in a combination that’s hearty, satisfying, and classically comforting. Just add a sprinkle of Parmesan over the top to take things toward Italian-style bliss.
